Storyline:

     This is the story of the methods used to defeat Hitler's V1 (doodlebug) and V2 (rocket) &quot;revenge weapons&quot; towards the end of the second world war. Even though the Nazis were in retreat these weapons could have turned their defeat into victory. The film includes references to Hannah Reich, who in real life was a German test pilot.



